{{lang|en|'''Gamescom'''}}（風格化書寫為{{lang|en|'''gamescom'''}}，在中文地区又被称为“科隆游戏展”或“GC展”）是一個在[[德國|德國]][[科隆|科隆]]舉行的年度遊戲交易展覽會。展覽會由Bundesverband Interaktive Unterhaltungssoftware組織舉辦。許多[[遊戲開發者|遊戲開發者]]都利用該展覽會展示他們即將發行的[[電子遊戲|電子遊戲]]和相關的硬件設備。<ref>{{cite web|title=Preliminary report on gamescom 2009: Cologne is ready for the premiere of the new leading European trade fair|url=http://www.gamescom-cologne.com/press/press_information.php?aktion=pfach&p1id=kmpresse_gamescom_e&format=html&base=&tp=k2&search=&pmid=kmeigen.kmpresse_1245772672&start=0&anzahl=10&channel=kmeigen&language=e}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezine.co.uk/news/formats/xbox360/lost-planet-2-make-ps3-debut-at-gamescom-$1318164.htm|title=Lost Planet 2 to make PS3 debut at GamesCom|date=2009-08-11|publisher=Game Zine|accessdate=2009-08-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090815202201/http://www.gamezine.co.uk/news/formats/xbox360/lost-planet-2-make-ps3-debut-at-gamescom-$1318164.htm|archivedate=2009-08-15}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://videogamesrepublic.com/?p=7999|title=Sony confirms unveiling of new Heavy Rain character for Gamescom|date=2009-08-11|publisher=Video Games Republic|accessdate=2009-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100131062259/http://videogamesrepublic.com/?p=7999|archive-date=2010-01-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/namco-bandai-partners--gamescom-line-up-tekken-6--dragon-ball--raging-blast--dragon-ball--revenge-of-king-piccolo--one-piece-unlimited-cruise-2--tales-of-symphonia-trade---dawn-of-the-new-world--family-trainer--extreme-challenge--katamari-forever-and-cham|title=Namco Bandai Partners' gamescom line-up|last=Namco Bandai Partners (Press release)|date=2009-08-07|accessdate=2009-08-11|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026134921/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/namco-bandai-partners--gamescom-line-up-tekken-6--dragon-ball--raging-blast--dragon-ball--revenge-of-king-piccolo--one-piece-unlimited-cruise-2--tales-of-symphonia-trade---dawn-of-the-new-world--family-trainer--extreme-challenge--katamari-forever-and-cham|dead-url=no}}</ref>

按照展會佔地和參觀人數計算，Gamescom是全歐最大的遊戲活動。根據其2014年數據，共有340,000參觀者、超過6,000位記者和來自88個國家共635個參展商參加了展會。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamescom-cologne.com/en/gamescom/presse/presseinformationen/gc_pressinformationen.php?aktion=pfach&p1id=kmpresse_gamescom_e&format=html&base=&tp=k3content&search=&pmid=kmeigen.kmpresse_1377444223&start=0&anzahl=10&channel=kmeigen&language=e&archiv=|title=No. 29 Final Report: Over 340,000 visitors celebrated the ʽnext generation of gamingʼ at the exceptional gamescom|publisher=gamescom.de|accessdate=2013-08-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130829010121/http://www.gamescom-cologne.com/en/gamescom/presse/presseinformationen/gc_pressinformationen.php?aktion=pfach&p1id=kmpresse_gamescom_e&format=html&base=&tp=k3content&search=&pmid=kmeigen.kmpresse_1377444223&start=0&anzahl=10&channel=kmeigen&language=e&archiv=|archivedate=2013-08-29}}</ref>{{third-party-inline|date=August 2013}}若按照總入場人數計算，德國Gamescom為世界第三的遊戲展，僅次於美國[[E3电子娱乐展|E3遊戲展]]及日本[[東京電玩展|東京電玩展]]。<ref name=asia1>{{cite web|url=http://www.destructoid.com/asia-game-show-beats-out-tgs-gamescom-in-attendance-218683.phtml|title=Asia Game Show beats out TGS, gamescom in attendance|publisher=Destructoid|accessdate=2014-08-09|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027175156/https://www.destructoid.com/asia-game-show-beats-out-tgs-gamescom-in-attendance-218683.phtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>德國Gamescom與美國[[E3电子娱乐展|E3遊戲展]]及日本[[東京電玩展|東京電玩展]]並列為世界三大遊戲展。

